Death's Activity Economy — Server Setup Guide

This guide explains how to set up server custom content for Death's Activity Economy aliases.

The aliases can use:

- Death's default GVAR content
- Server custom SVAR content
- Both together

Servers can also choose whether players see everything by default, or only content unlocked in their character CVAR.

staminaSettings:
  mode: daily
  max: 100
  reset_hour: 0
  timezone_offset: -5
  interval_minutes: 0
  regen_amount: 0

This controls stamina refresh only.

"mode: daily" means stamina resets to full once per server day.

"mode: regen" means stamina regenerates over time using "interval_minutes" and "regen_amount".

Source Control SVAR

Create this server svar:

activitySources

Example:

useGvar: true
useSvar: false
priority: svar
unlockMode: all
unlockCvar: activity_unlocks
setupGuideUrl: https://github.com/YOURNAME/YOURREPO/blob/main/activity-server-setup.md

Source Options

useGvar: true
useSvar: false

Uses Death's default GVAR content only.

useGvar: false
useSvar: true

Uses server custom SVAR content only.

useGvar: true
useSvar: true

Uses both Death's default GVAR content and server custom SVAR content.

Priority

priority: svar

If a duplicate item or recipe exists in both the GVAR and SVAR, the server SVAR version wins.

priority: gvar

If a duplicate item or recipe exists in both the GVAR and SVAR, the default GVAR version wins.

Unlock Mode

unlockMode: all

All enabled content is visible and usable.

unlockMode: unlocked

Only content listed in the character's unlock CVAR is visible and usable.

The default unlock CVAR is:

activity_unlocks

Example character CVAR:

[
  "Copper Ore",
  "Iron Ore",
  "Silver Ore",
  "fish:*",
  "mine:junk",
  "bread:*",
  "moonsteel_smithing"
]

Fixed Server Content SVAR Names

The aliases check these fixed svar names:

activityServerItems
activityServerMaterials
activityServerComponents
activityServerRecipes
activityServerGathering
activityServerOverrides

Servers should use these exact names.

activityServerItems

Use this for general items.

items:
  Moonsteel Dagger:
    name: Moonsteel Dagger
    category: weapon
    value_cp: 25000
    description: A pale silver-blue dagger made from moonsteel.
    image: https://example.com/moonsteel-dagger.png

activityServerMaterials

Use this for raw materials.

materials:
  Moonsteel Ore:
    name: Moonsteel Ore
    category: ore
    value_cp: 2000
    description: Rare silver-blue ore found under moonlit stone.

  Moonsteel Ingot:
    name: Moonsteel Ingot
    category: metal
    value_cp: 5000
    description: A refined ingot used in rare smithing recipes.

activityServerComponents

Use this for crafted parts and intermediate components.

components:
  Fine Leather Wrap:
    name: Fine Leather Wrap
    category: weapon component
    value_cp: 250
    description: Treated leather used for grips and handles.

  Weapon Handle:
    name: Weapon Handle
    category: weapon component
    value_cp: 100
    description: A prepared handle suitable for simple weapons.

activityServerRecipes

Use this for crafting, smithing, weaving, alchemy, bakery, and make recipes.

recipes:
  Moonsteel Dagger:
    name: Moonsteel Dagger
    activity: smithing
    category: weapon
    dc: 16
    cost_gp: 250
    unlock: moonsteel_smithing
    materials:
      Moonsteel Ingot: 1
      Weapon Handle: 1
      Fine Leather Wrap: 1
    result:
      name: Moonsteel Dagger
      qty: 1

activityServerGathering

Use this for custom gathering results for fish, mine, forage, bug, wood, track, and similar aliases.

gathering:
  mine:
    items:
      Moonsteel Ore:
        name: Moonsteel Ore
        category: ore
        rarity: rare
        dc: 18
        weight: 2
        value_cp: 2000
        description: Rare silver-blue ore found under moonlit stone.

  fish:
    items:
      Glassfin Trout:
        name: Glassfin Trout
        category: fish
        rarity: uncommon
        dc: 14
        weight: 5
        value_cp: 80
        description: A translucent river fish with shimmering fins.

activityServerOverrides

Use this to disable, replace, or adjust default content without editing the aliases.

disabled:
  - Wish Potion
  - Dragonbone Plate

overrides:
  Iron Dagger:
    dc: 14
    cost_gp: 10

Unlock Examples

Unlock one exact item:

Copper Ore

Unlock all fishing content:

fish:*

Unlock all mining junk content:

mine:junk

Unlock all bread recipes or items:

bread:*

Unlock recipes requiring a special key:

moonsteel_smithing

Recommended Setups

Default System Only

useGvar: true
useSvar: false
priority: svar
unlockMode: all
unlockCvar: activity_unlocks

Server Custom Content Only

useGvar: false
useSvar: true
priority: svar
unlockMode: all
unlockCvar: activity_unlocks

Default + Server Custom Content

useGvar: true
useSvar: true
priority: svar
unlockMode: all
unlockCvar: activity_unlocks

Locked Progression Mode

useGvar: true
useSvar: true
priority: svar
unlockMode: unlocked
unlockCvar: activity_unlocks
